@tenzo.cannabis Super Sativa❣️

Lineage: Boost x Tangelo 
( From what I found on Reddit cuz the strain name nor lineage is listed on the product, OCS, or their website>:( ..) 

Tenzo provides us with a small batch pheno-hunted & handcrafted sativa - indoor grown, hang dried & 🤚-trimmed cultivar with a very unique terp profile. 

Total Terp % 3.04: Myrcene, Limonene, Caryophyllene & others. 

Effects & Experience - brings a uniquely creative & euphoric uplifted vibe to my 🧠 while still providing my body with a slightly more sedative & relaxed experience 😌 Good for a midday mood boost ⚡️ If you tend to feel more anxious with sativa strains this one might be your go to with Myrcene being the dominant terp, it’s known for being very relaxing & is probably why it felt more like a laid-back kinda vibe. 

Taste & Smell 👅 - Superrrr sweet candy 🍬 & lemon with some pungent spice & musk undertones. Easy on the inhale & exhale 😮‍💨 Overall, I’m very interested in elevating my experience & trying out different cultivars 🍃 by this craft company! Let me know if you’ve tried it out & how your experience was. 🫶
